    public class NumberBox<T>
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ValueBox<T>
    Base class to handle number values on <input type="number"> elements.

    The parsing and formatting is done by the browser, using the user specific i18n settings.

    Author:
    gilberto-torrezan
    See Also:
    MaterialNumberBox
